{"tid":1770951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"勞處被指受壓 停製二噁英安全指引","createTime":"2019-12-05T13:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T13:22:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"71070ede4b0cade8264d5a6f19d82eb6dc3c9684","tid":1770951,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191205/FNUMVLCO3V7OTBOQOQ5M6BSGVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191205%2FFNUMVLCO3V7OTBOQOQ5M6BSGVU%2F&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=2b2b2e23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191205%2FFNUMVLCO3V7OTBOQOQ5M6BSGVU%2F&h=52c7dd7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191205/FNUMVLCO3V7OTBOQOQ5M6BSGVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n勞處被指受壓 停製二噁英安全指引<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191205/large/1575476917_ec8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191205%2Flarge%2F1575476917_ec8e.jpg&h=6af73cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅致光沒有回應勞工處疑受政治壓力停製催淚煙安全指引的指控。李家皓攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】護老院等社福機構多次受催淚煙波及，有立法會議員得悉勞工處在政治壓力下，煞停製作針對僱員的催淚煙安全指引，勞工及福利局局長羅致光未有正面回應，指院舍只有輕微不適個案，反引述文獻指燒烤產生的二噁英遠高於催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：濫權纍纍 指揮官稱無用過份武力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅致光稱BBQ釋二噁英更高<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員朱凱廸昨於立法會會議上表示，曾親耳聽聞勞工處副處長梁永恩指，勞工處因應公眾對催淚煙的關注，製作針對社福機構勞工在內的一般僱員安全指引，惟近日得悉處方受政治壓力，擱置推出指引。羅致光未有正面回應指控是否屬實，僅稱衞生署及食環署推出相關指引前，均有徵詢勞工處意見。<br />\n<br />\n工黨立法會議員張超雄關注6月至今有多宗安老及復康服務單位人士，因吸入催淚煙不適的個案，羅致光回應稱，社署得悉目前只有輕微不適個案，包括接觸催淚煙後有輕微呼吸系統及皮膚不適，但沒有嚴重個案，毋須再深入調查，又指可安排外展醫生為受影響安老院等住客診治，但局方沒有統計受影響人數。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員陸頌雄則關注，示威者燃燒雜物產生有毒物質，並堵路影響社福機構服務使用者出行，甚至構成心理影響。羅致光指示威者燒一般垃圾或膠欄杆，有關物質含有PVC，所產生的二噁英數量比催淚煙多以百倍計，又指文獻資料顯示催淚煙產生二噁英是絕無僅有、十分低，「燒任何嘢，包括燒烤產生嘅二噁英都遠遠高過催淚煙。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然"},{"pid":"7a0bf94d6a660ed327c41365b38a556e9a6e1db6","tid":1770951,"uid":2076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"868c6e7f3a87838273aa8c9d9b18560a4ec80df3","tid":1770951,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"56239247db01e2b402e062bcc8d6c721bc71ad8d","tid":1770951,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487c2906f404664c9fd2606b761a5cd71408138f","tid":1770951,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a0bf94d6a660ed327c41365b38a556e9a6e1db6","tid":1770951,"uid":2076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"【第十陸期牆紙】回首、向前<br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWMVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=ad1f9438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwsVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwsVSd.jpg&h=bc013387&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16bea7b03c2e1de146a4e1f3ba187f3ef237389b","tid":1770951,"uid":65354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"果日開會梁永恩嘅講法係好多市民大眾關注勞工應對催淚彈嘅措施，所以先會研究指引<br />\n<br />\n大家得閒就用僱員身份問下奴工處返工遇到放tg點算好 自己要點做 僱主應該要點做"}]}